text: Harry Jacobs (21 December 1913 – 15 February 2000) was a former Australian rules footballer who played with Fitzroy and Hawthorn in the Victorian Football League (VFL). == Notes == == External links == * * Category:1913 births Category:2000 deaths Category:Australian rules footballers from Victoria (Australia) Category:Fitzroy Football Club players Category:Hawthorn Football Club players
